===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|舛|囗|ls=ic}} – footsteps around an enclosure. Possibly the original character for {{och-l|圍|to surround}} and {{och-l|衛|to guard}}. Phonetically borrowed to indicate "tanned leather".

The footprint on top is stylized as [[𫝀]], which is similar but unrelated to [[五]].

